 In this manuscript, I introduce a clear and succinct text file format for
 describing the layout of wells on microplates.
 Compared to other methods of annotating these experiments, the wellmap
 file format is easier to read, easier to write, easier to share, easier
 to check for mistakes, and easier to incorporate into analysis scripts.
